.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, milk, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, pop, indie, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the fan of indie is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
 2. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
 5. the fan of trance is not the person drinking milk##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 9. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk          | coffee      | water      | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre        | indie     | trance | pop | disco      |
| Sport      | weightlifting | baseball    | badminton  | ice-hockey |

