.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, plum, potato
City: san-francisco, nizza, miami, boston
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, colombian, dutch
 1. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 2. the person traveling to boston is not the brazilian##6
 3. the colombian is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person traveling to boston##7
 4. the brazilian is not to the left of the person traveling to nizza##8
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the colombian is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 8. the dutch is between the person eating blueberry and the colombian##2
 9. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the american is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapes      | plum      | potato | blueberry |
| City   | miami | san-francisco    | boston | nizza     |
| Nationality   | american    | colombian | dutch  | brazilian |

