 8. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the polish##8
 9. the polish is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
10. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
11. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the polish##8
12. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
13. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbellflower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4      |
