House: cottage, tower, art-deco, townhouse
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating lime##5
2. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating lime and the person eating cucumber##7
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
4. the art-deco house is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the person eating lime is the tower house##1
8. the person eating lime is somewhere between the townhouse house and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the person eating lime is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | coffee | iced-tea  | soy-milk |
| Food          | cranberry | lime   | asparagus | cucumber |
| House   | cottage     | tower   | townhouse      | art-deco      |

