 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the scientist##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
 9. the designer is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
10. the person driving the ship is not to the left of the designer##8
11. the german is not to the left of the photographer##8
12. the designer is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
14. the photographer is on the left of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
