The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 2. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
 3. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
 4. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
 5. the person eating cranberry is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
 6. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person eating cranberry is not to the right of the person who likes ivory##8
11. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food        | cabbage    | watermelon  | pepper     | cranberry |
| Color       | light-blue     | fuchsia | black | ivory   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | scooter     | helicopter | roller    |

