.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, august, april
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, snowboarding, swimming
1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the person who's sport is swimming is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is handball##7
8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | october | december     | april  | august |
| Pet           | fish      | snake        | rabbit   | chinchilla |
| Sport         | handball  | snowboarding | swimming | golf       |

 